.SH "Detailed Description"
.PP 
\fBProgram\fP class to abstract OpenGL \fBShader\fP Programs\&. 


.PP
\fBWarning\fP
.RS 4
\fBProgram\fP must be deconstructed before the OpenGL context is destroyed\&. 

.PP
This class is not guaranteed to be thread-safe\&.
.RE
.PP
\fBNote\fP
.RS 4
This class owns the underlying OpenGL \fBProgram\fP object and releases it upon destruction or \fBreset()\fP\&. 
.RE
.PP

