.SS "void egl::Program::attach (const \fBShader\fP & shader)"

.PP
Attaches \fBShader\fP to \fBProgram\fP for linking\&. 
.PP
\fBNote\fP
.RS 4
Attaching a \fBShader\fP invalidates the current link state\&.
.RE
.PP
\fBWarning\fP
.RS 4
Attaching a destroyed \fBShader\fP is undefined behavior\&. 

.PP
Attached Shaders must outlive the \fBProgram\fP (at least until linking)\&.
.RE
.PP
\fBExceptions\fP
.RS 4
\fIstd::runtime_error\fP If the \fBShader\fP has already been attached\&. 
.br
\fIstd::logic_error\fP If the current \fBProgram\fP object does not exist (\fBreset()\fP is recommended to return to a valid state)\&.
.RE
.PP
\fBParameters\fP
.RS 4
\fIshader\fP The \fBShader\fP that should be attached to the \fBProgram\fP\&. 
.RE
